'text': 'I was shocked to see the lump of foam on the macchiato, we weren’t looking for master latte art, but a white blob is not acceptable 🙁. We have dropped by numerous times, both for breakfast and sometimes even for a late-night snack. One of the advantages of this coffee shop is its convenient location near our gym, making it easily accessible for us. It's a relief to have such a spot nearby where we can unwind and enjoy a satisfying meal. However, it's important to note that the coffee shop closes at 11:30 pm, so it may not be the best option for those looking for late-night dining. During our visits, we usually indulge in their delectable desserts, often opting for two slices of their delicious cakes. The quality of the desserts is consistently good, and we always leave satisfied. Moreover, what sets this coffee shop apart is its friendly staff, fast service, and clean and spacious dining area. The welcoming atmosphere adds to the overall pleasant experience. However, the only challenge we face when visiting this coffee shop is finding a parking spot. Due to its location in a busy area, parking can be quite challenging at times. It requires a bit of patience and persistence to secure a spot, especially during peak hours. Despite the parking inconvenience, we continue to frequent this coffee shop because of its friendly staff, quick service, clean environment, and tasty desserts.
